522
00:30:55,069 --> 00:30:56,370
Why did this happen?

523
00:30:56,371 --> 00:30:58,873
Why? Tell me!

524
00:30:58,873 --> 00:31:00,741
Captain!

525
00:31:02,710 --> 00:31:06,347
You listen to me. You better pray nothing happens to him;

526
00:31:06,347 --> 00:31:09,017
