529
00:31:12,153 --> 00:31:13,855
- Tang Yi!
- Captain, calm down.

530
00:31:13,855 --> 00:31:16,756
Let me go!

531
00:31:39,214 --> 00:31:40,914
Tang Yi,

532
00:31:40,915 --> 00:31:43,251
I'm sorry.

533
00:31:48,055 --> 00:31:49,824
I'm sorry.

534
00:31:53,494 --> 00:31:56,163
I'm sorry.

535
00:32:03,004 --> 00:32:05,306
I'm sorry.

536
00:32:09,777 --> 00:32:11,778
How could this happen?

537
00:32:11,779 --> 00:32:14,281
He went to protect Tang Yi.

538
00:32:14,282 --> 00:32:17,885
