546
00:32:42,310 --> 00:32:43,944
Yes.

547
00:32:43,945 --> 00:32:47,081
I think after the Captain finishes this cup, I'll take him home first.

548
00:32:47,081 --> 00:32:49,851
He was on duty all night yesterday and hasn't slept,

549
00:32:49,851 --> 00:32:52,085
and not in a good mood.

550
00:32:52,086 --> 00:32:53,120
Let's go.

551
00:32:53,121 --> 00:32:54,989
Sure.

552
00:33:05,533 --> 00:33:07,668
Yuchi.

553
00:33:07,669 --> 00:33:09,703
Are you okay?

554
00:33:09,704 --> 00:33:12,306
The surgery's over.

555
00:33:12,307 --> 00:33:14,308
The doctor said it went well.

556
00:33:14,309 --> 00:33:17,345
