565
00:33:34,028 --> 00:33:35,531
- Thank you.
- No problem.

566
00:33:35,531 --> 00:33:36,630
Captain, your tea.

567
00:33:36,631 --> 00:33:39,434
Excuse me. Can we go in to see him?

568
00:33:39,434 --> 00:33:41,770
Not yet. You need to wait until he's in the general ward.

569
00:33:41,770 --> 00:33:43,838
Okay.

570
00:33:45,039 --> 00:33:48,108
This time, this punk was lucky the fates were on his side.

571
00:33:48,109 --> 00:33:50,778
