582
00:34:20,241 --> 00:34:22,342
to be extra careful and cautious of your own safety.

583
00:34:22,343 --> 00:34:24,947
I don't want to see anyone get hurt. Understand?

584
00:34:24,947 --> 00:34:26,947
Yes.

585
00:34:30,018 --> 00:34:32,487
Once A-fei gets moved to the general ward, call me.

586
00:34:32,487 --> 00:34:34,220
Yes.

587
00:34:45,066 --> 00:34:45,900
Boss!

588
00:34:45,900 --> 00:34:46,634
Where is he?

589
00:34:46,635 --> 00:34:48,236
Inside.

590
00:34:53,841 --> 00:34:55,675
Get out.

591
00:34:55,676 --> 00:34:56,845
Boss, let me handle it. Don't get your hands dirty.

592
00:34:56,845 --> 00:34:59,212
Get out.

593
00:34:59,213 --> 00:35:00,914
