Don't.

599
00:35:23,137 --> 00:35:23,938
Sorry.

600
00:35:23,939 --> 00:35:25,505
Spare me.

601
00:35:25,506 --> 00:35:27,508
Sorry.

602
00:35:29,243 --> 00:35:30,811
I hope you can resist for a long time

603
00:35:30,812 --> 00:35:33,448
because I'm going to do my best.

604
00:35:35,783 --> 00:35:37,320
Don't.

605
00:35:39,954 --> 00:35:42,256
Don't.

606
00:35:45,726 --> 00:35:48,796
Don't. I know I was wrong!

607
00:35:48,796 --> 00:35:50,965
No need to tell me now. I'll take my time.

608
00:35:50,965 --> 00:35:51,632
Sorry!

609
00:35:51,633 --> 00:35:52,732
Let me see how long you can last.

610
00:35:52,733 --> 00:35:53,501
I really didn't know!

611
00:35:53,502 --> 00:35:54,801
Then don't say anything.

612
00:35:54,802 --> 00:35:56,137
I don't need to know.

613
00:35:56,137 --> 00:35:58,138
Relax.

614
00:35:58,139 --> 00:36:00,107
He won't kill him.

615
00:36:00,108 --> 00:36:02,875
The Boss still understands this principle.

616
00:36:02,877 --> 00:36:05,847
Why should I be worried about that punk?

617
00:36:05,847 --> 00:36:07,447
Then I misunderstood.

618
00:36:07,448 --> 00:36:09,550
I saw you getting so nervous.

619
00:36:10,184 --> 00:36:12,185
I thought you knew each other.

620
00:36:12,186 --> 00:36:13,587
What do you mean?

621
00:36:13,588 --> 00:36:15,288
What do you mean by we know each other?

622
00:36:15,289 --> 00:36:16,756
Who the hell is he?

623
00:36:16,757 --> 00:36:18,625
Will I know this kind of little punk?

624
00:36:18,626 --> 00:36:23,494
Brother De, is it necessary for you to be this angry?

625
00:36:23,494 --> 00:36:27,632
I'm just casually saying. You're just casually listening.

626
00:36:28,636 --> 00:36:31,970
Some things shouldn't even be casually spoken.

627
00:36:32,006 --> 00:36:35,039
Also, be careful of your knife.

628
00:36:41,890 --> 00:36:43,450
I'm so sorry!

629
00:36:43,450 --> 00:36:45,590
I'm sorry toward him!

630
00:37:07,275 --> 00:37:09,309
Why did you take so long before returning my message?

631
00:37:09,310 --> 00:37:11,746
The Boss already caught the guy.

632
00:37:14,916 --> 00:37:16,850
Are you trying to get me killed?

633
00:37:16,851 --> 00:37:18,652
No!

634
00:37:19,353 --> 00:37:21,954
The plan was executed as I reported it to you.

635
00:37:21,954 --> 00:37:24,723
Making it look like someone is putting pressure on the upcoming bid.

636
00:37:24,725 --> 00:37:27,326
Also, I instructed them to only use bats

637
00:37:27,326 --> 00:37:30,295
to teach Meng Shaofei a lesson and make it look like he can't protect anyone,

638
00:37:30,298 --> 00:37:31,966
that's all.

639
00:37:32,833 --> 00:37:34,834
Bats?

640
00:37:34,835 --> 00:37:37,237
But they used guns.

641
00:37:37,238 --> 00:37:39,339
Previously, you said you can get rid of Meng Shaofei,

642
00:37:39,340 --> 00:37:41,208
so I reluctantly cooperated.

643
00:37:41,209 --> 00:37:44,711
Now that you let things get this far,

644
00:37:44,712 --> 00:37:47,979
or do you have other motives?

645
00:37:47,982 --> 00:37:49,249
I--

646
00:37:49,250 --> 00:37:52,850
Director Zuo, all these years, I've been with Boss and did so many things,

647
00:37:52,850 --> 00:37:55,222
there's no way I would do this!

648
00:37:55,223 --> 00:37:59,090
Furthermore, I really don't know why things turned out like this.

649
00:37:59,090 --> 00:38:00,894
I called my people to confirm and

650
00:38:00,895 --> 00:38:04,065
before my guys got there, it already happened.

651
00:38:04,065 --> 00:38:07,034
I really didn't send that person there.

652
00:38:09,036 --> 00:38:10,770
I was going to say

653
00:38:10,771 --> 00:38:14,140
that this punk, I'll handle myself.

654
00:38:14,140 --> 00:38:17,508
But I never thought that the Boss insisted on asking himself.

655
00:38:17,578 --> 00:38:20,848
And he's even doing it personally.

656
00:38:22,316 --> 00:38:25,186
Director Zuo, I never thought that

657
00:38:25,186 --> 00:38:29,153
the Boss would react to Meng Shaofei getting injured so dramatically.

658
00:38:34,262 --> 00:38:37,698
Anyway, my part in cooperating with your show ends here.

659
00:38:37,698 --> 00:38:40,932
If that punk were to inadvertently say something,

660
00:38:40,932 --> 00:38:43,169
you're on your own.

661
00:38:43,170 --> 00:38:44,672
Director Zuo!

662
00:38:57,718 --> 00:39:00,054
We sent the guy to Dr. Jiang.

663
00:39:03,691 --> 00:39:07,492
Boss, who sent him?

664
00:39:10,698 --> 00:39:12,432
Just out of pure curiosity,

665
00:39:12,433 --> 00:39:15,234
