666
00:39:22,810 --> 00:39:25,446
Chen Wenhao.

667
00:39:37,325 --> 00:39:39,026
What are you doing following me?

668
00:39:39,994 --> 00:39:43,194
We already found out who sent them.

669
00:39:46,767 --> 00:39:48,836
Chen Wenhao.

670
00:39:49,837 --> 00:39:52,239
I already told Tang Yi to be careful.

671
00:39:53,341 --> 00:39:55,942
And now Chen Wenhao really made a move.

672
00:39:58,145 --> 00:40:02,350
Miss, this time was all luck.

673
00:40:04,785 --> 00:40:06,987
