674
00:40:07,822 --> 00:40:09,857
We would be very worried.

675
00:40:15,363 --> 00:40:17,865
That cop isn't one of us.

676
00:40:19,800 --> 00:40:23,535
That's something that the Boss needs to worry about, not you.

677
00:40:26,273 --> 00:40:29,642
Since Tang Yi met that cop,

678
00:40:29,643 --> 00:40:32,045
nothing good has come of it.

679
00:40:32,046 --> 00:40:35,649
I used my own way to protect him. What right do you have to criticize me?

680
00:40:35,649 --> 00:40:38,683
The way Boss reacted to him, I'm sure you saw it, too.

681
00:40:39,820 --> 00:40:44,188
Meng Shaofei is different.

682
00:40:44,191 --> 00:40:47,093
If you really care for Boss,

683
00:40:47,094 --> 00:40:49,063
you need to let him handle it on his own.

684
00:40:50,264 --> 00:40:53,000
I don't want to see you get hurt.

685
00:40:55,169 --> 00:40:58,239
You don't want to see me get hurt?

686
00:40:59,373 --> 00:41:02,343
Do you know who hurts me the most?

687
00:41:04,845 --> 00:41:07,548
It's you, Gu Daoyi.

688
00:41:13,320 --> 00:41:16,321
- I'll take you home.
- No, you're dodging again.

689
00:41:17,858 --> 00:41:21,825
Why is it that every time this subject comes up, you dodge the subject?

690
00:41:21,825 --> 00:41:25,396
