696
00:41:46,353 --> 00:41:48,855
After all, I have taken care of you for so many years.

697
00:41:48,856 --> 00:41:51,658
So, you've misunderstood that this was a feeling of like.

698
00:41:51,659 --> 00:41:54,561
I don't misunderstand.

699
00:41:54,562 --> 00:41:56,262
