703
00:42:06,474 --> 00:42:07,974
Miss.

704
00:42:07,975 --> 00:42:10,144
You're right.

705
00:42:11,245 --> 00:42:12,445
I'm a habit.

706
00:42:12,446 --> 00:42:15,049
