711
00:42:29,464 --> 00:42:31,364
Don't come any closer.

712
00:42:31,365 --> 00:42:35,466
You being nice to me is just something that Tang Yi asked you to do, isn't it?

713
00:42:39,707 --> 00:42:42,109
